{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#5603: `Teleport` component's DOM isn't unmounted when deactivated inside `KeepAlive`",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:33.747336+00:00",
  "text": "`Teleport` component's DOM isn't unmounted when deactivated inside `KeepAlive`\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.31\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[codesandbox.io](https://codesandbox.io/s/determined-silence-kbwsve?file=/src/App.vue)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nClick 'show modal' then click 'to tab2'.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nModal's DOM removed.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nModal's DOM isn't removed.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
